practitioner.about:
Dr. Farah Kitana is a Specialist in Internal Medicine at Medcare Medical Centre. She completed her MD degree from the University of Jordan Medical School, an Internship in Internal Medicine from Al-Istishari Hospital, Jordan, and a Residency in Internal Medicine from Medstar Georgetown University Hospital, Washington, DC. She is a member of the American College of Physicians.

Dr. Kitana commenced her career in Internal Medicine at Medstar Georgetown University Hospital in Washington, DC, and then relocated to the UAE to join Medcare. Her expertise covers obesity and weight management, nutritional education, women's health, geriatric disease, chronic disease management, primary and preventive care, immunisation and travel medicine. She has proficiently treated patients with hypertension, diabetes, thyroid disease, high cholesterol, asthma, upper and lower respiratory tract infections, urinary tract infections, headaches and anaemia.

Dr. Kitana believes in keeping fit by practicing Yoga and hiking during her spare time. She also enjoys playing the piano. She speaks Arabic and English.

locations.about:
Medcare Medical Centre in Arabian Ranches 3 stands as a premium, advanced healthcare facility devoted to meeting the diverse healthcare needs of its community. This inviting medical centre prioritizes comfort and convenience, providing cutting-edge facilities and comprehensive medical services all under one roof. Ideal for patients of every age seeking precise diagnoses and prompt treatment across various specialties.

At the helm of Medcare Medical Centre Arabian Ranches 3 is a team of multicultural, multilingual doctors, complemented by exceptionally-trained and experienced nurses and medical staff. The centre takes pride in its extensive array of state-of-the-art equipment, empowering its highly skilled medical team to deliver a premium level of care to all patients.

Experience the warmth of family-centric care delivered by our highly talented medical and non-medical staff. At Medcare Medical Centre Arabian Ranches 3, we offer a range of services, including Internal Medicine, Gynaecology, Paediatrics, Dermatology & Aesthetics, ENT, General Medicine and Physiotherapy.

As part of our commitment to accessible healthcare, Medcare operates a network of four hospitals and 22 plus multi-specialty clinics across Dubai and Sharjah. Our goal is to provide reliable and timely medical care to our diverse clientele.

Great News! We are expanding to better suit all your medical and beauty needs!
